title: Lynyrd Skynyrd - Gold and Platinum - 320kmps MP3
description:
Lynyrd Skynrd's "Greatest Hits", sort of.  A very good collection of some of their best works, all carefully ripped to MP3, 320 kbps using DBpowerAmp's ripping functionality.  All rips had status "accurate" as tested against other rips and the original.

After seeing the dearth of Lynyrd Skynard material out there, I decided to do something about it.  These are some of my first attempts at creating a torrent, but I've made every effort to provide the best quality and the least redundancy in the torrent universe.

Brought to you by the artists and the one and only Zygon - this has been my nom de plume since the mid-nineties!
